title: Zahrada
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Indian, Macrobiotic, Organic, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. This restaurant has options for vegans and those on a gluten free plan. Uses organic / local when possible. They use tempeh, tofu, bulgur, quinoa, to name a few. Non-smoking environment. Wi-fi.
